<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/931537-is-a-knowledge-of-roman-history-before">Is a knowledge of Roman history (before the period in this book, or in general) necessary to appreciate the book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_931537'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F91017.Rubicon">like</a></span>

