</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/4631805-dave-hill">***Dave Hill</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Having some basic knowledge certainly wouldn&apos;t hurt, but really isn&apos;t necessary. This is a pretty popular history, and very accessible. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Having some basic knowledge certainly wouldn't hurt, but really isn't necessary. This is a pretty popular history, and very accessible. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
